#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:1
msgid "Git Sync"
msgstr "Git 동기화"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:3
msgid ""
"The **CxFlow Git Sync** (`lu_cxflow_git_sync`) module enables "
"bidirectional synchronization between CxFlow documents and Git "
"repositories."
msgstr ""
"**CxFlow Git Sync** (`lu_cxflow_git_sync`) 모듈은 CxFlow 문서와 Git "
"저장소 간의 양방향 동기화를 지원합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:6
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "개요"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:14
msgid ""
"Documents are stored as Markdown files in the Git repository, preserving "
"the SSOT principle — what you see in CxFlow is what you get in Git."
msgstr ""
"문서는 Git 저장소에 Markdown 파일로 저장되어 SSOT 원칙을 유지합니다 — "
"CxFlow에서 보는 것이 Git에서도 동일합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:17
msgid "Setting Up a Git Repository"
msgstr "Git 저장소 설정"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:19
msgid "Navigate to **CxFlow → Git Sync → Repositories** and create a new record."
msgstr "**CxFlow → Git Sync → Repositories**로 이동하여 새 레코드를 생성합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:21
msgid "Configuration Fields"
msgstr "설정 필드"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8 ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:59
#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "Field"
msgstr "필드"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8 ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:59
#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "Description"
msgstr "설명"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "Required"
msgstr "필수"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "**Repository URL**"
msgstr "**저장소 URL**"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "HTTPS or SSH URL"
msgstr "HTTPS 또는 SSH URL"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "예"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "**Branch**"
msgstr "**브랜치**"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "Target branch (default: `main`)"
msgstr "대상 브랜치 (기본값: `main`)"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "**Auth Method**"
msgstr "**인증 방식**"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "`none`, `pat` (Personal Access Token), `ssh`"
msgstr "`none`, `pat` (Personal Access Token), `ssh`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "**Access Token**"
msgstr "**액세스 토큰**"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "Token for HTTPS auth"
msgstr "HTTPS 인증용 토큰"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "If PAT"
msgstr "PAT인 경우"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "**SSH Key Path**"
msgstr "**SSH 키 경로**"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "Server path to SSH key"
msgstr "서버의 SSH 키 경로"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "If SSH"
msgstr "SSH인 경우"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "**Auto Push**"
msgstr "**자동 Push**"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "Push to Git on every document save"
msgstr "문서 저장 시마다 Git에 Push"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "No"
msgstr "아니오"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "**Auto Pull (Cron)**"
msgstr "**자동 Pull (Cron)**"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "Periodically pull from Git"
msgstr "주기적으로 Git에서 Pull"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "**Sync Scope**"
msgstr "**동기화 범위**"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:8
msgid "`all`, `cps`, `deliverable`, `report`, `note`"
msgstr "`all`, `cps`, `deliverable`, `report`, `note`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:35
msgid ""
"Auto Push and Auto Pull are mutually exclusive — enable one or the other "
"to avoid sync conflicts."
msgstr ""
"Auto Push와 Auto Pull은 상호 배타적입니다 — 동기화 충돌을 방지하려면 "
"둘 중 하나만 활성화하세요."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:39
msgid "Constraint"
msgstr "제약 조건"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:41
msgid "Only one Git repository can be configured per project."
msgstr "프로젝트당 하나의 Git 저장소만 설정할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:43
msgid "Sync Operations"
msgstr "동기화 작업"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:45
msgid "Test Connection"
msgstr "연결 테스트"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:47
msgid ""
"Click **Test Connection** to validate credentials and confirm the "
"repository is accessible. This clones the repo to a temporary directory."
msgstr ""
"**Test Connection**을 클릭하여 자격 증명을 검증하고 저장소 접근 가능 여부를 "
"확인합니다. 임시 디렉토리에 저장소를 클론합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:50
msgid "Full Export"
msgstr "전체 내보내기"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:52
msgid ""
"**Full Export** pushes all project documents (filtered by sync scope) to "
"the Git repository in a single operation. Use this for initial setup."
msgstr ""
"**전체 내보내기**는 모든 프로젝트 문서(동기화 범위로 필터링)를 한 번의 "
"작업으로 Git 저장소에 Push합니다. 초기 설정에 사용하세요."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:55
msgid "Full Import"
msgstr "전체 가져오기"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:57
msgid "**Full Import** pulls all documents from Git and overwrites local content."
msgstr "**전체 가져오기**는 Git에서 모든 문서를 Pull하여 로컬 콘텐츠를 덮어씁니다."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:60
msgid ""
"Full Import overwrites local `md_source`. Use with caution — consider "
"exporting first as a backup."
msgstr ""
"전체 가져오기는 로컬 `md_source`를 덮어씁니다. 주의해서 사용하세요 — "
"백업으로 먼저 내보내기를 고려하세요."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:64
msgid "Auto Push"
msgstr "자동 Push"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:66
msgid ""
"When `auto_push` is enabled, every document save triggers an automatic "
"Git push for that document. The mixin extension tracks:"
msgstr ""
"`auto_push`가 활성화되면 문서 저장 시마다 해당 문서에 대한 자동 Git Push가 "
"트리거됩니다. 믹스인 확장은 다음을 추적합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:59
msgid "`git_sync_path`"
msgstr "`git_sync_path`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:59
msgid "File path in the repository"
msgstr "저장소 내 파일 경로"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:59
msgid "`git_sync_sha`"
msgstr "`git_sync_sha`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:59
msgid "SHA-256 hash (first 16 chars) of `md_source`"
msgstr "`md_source`의 SHA-256 해시 (앞 16자)"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:59
msgid "`git_last_synced_at`"
msgstr "`git_last_synced_at`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:59
msgid "Timestamp of last sync"
msgstr "마지막 동기화 타임스탬프"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:59
msgid "`git_last_synced_version`"
msgstr "`git_last_synced_version`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:59
msgid "Document version at last sync"
msgstr "마지막 동기화 시 문서 버전"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:76
msgid "Auto Pull (Cron)"
msgstr "자동 Pull (Cron)"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:78
msgid ""
"When `auto_pull_cron` is enabled, the hourly cron job automatically pulls"
" changes from the repository."
msgstr ""
"`auto_pull_cron`이 활성화되면 매시간 크론 작업이 자동으로 저장소에서 "
"변경사항을 Pull합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:81
msgid "State Machine"
msgstr "상태 머신"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:93
msgid ""
"The cron job also recovers stuck repositories — if a repo has been in "
"`syncing` state for more than 10 minutes, it is automatically reset."
msgstr ""
"크론 작업은 중단된 저장소도 복구합니다 — 저장소가 10분 이상 `syncing` "
"상태에 있으면 자동으로 초기화됩니다."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:96
msgid "Sync Log"
msgstr "동기화 로그"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:98
msgid "Every sync operation creates a log entry in `lu.cxflow.git.sync.log`:"
msgstr "모든 동기화 작업은 `lu.cxflow.git.sync.log`에 로그 항목을 생성합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "`direction`"
msgstr "`direction`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "`export` or `import`"
msgstr "`export` 또는 `import`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "`state`"
msgstr "`state`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "`success`, `conflict`, `error`"
msgstr "`success`, `conflict`, `error`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "`doc_model` / `doc_id`"
msgstr "`doc_model` / `doc_id`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "Affected document"
msgstr "영향받은 문서"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "`file_path`"
msgstr "`file_path`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "Path in Git repository"
msgstr "Git 저장소 내 경로"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "`commit_sha`"
msgstr "`commit_sha`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "Git commit hash"
msgstr "Git 커밋 해시"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "`db_version`"
msgstr "`db_version`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "Document version at sync time"
msgstr "동기화 시 문서 버전"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:109
msgid ""
"Use the log to diagnose sync issues and track document change history "
"across both systems."
msgstr ""
"로그를 사용하여 동기화 문제를 진단하고 양쪽 시스템에 걸친 문서 변경 이력을 "
"추적합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:112
msgid "Cron Job"
msgstr "크론 작업"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "Cron"
msgstr "크론"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "Schedule"
msgstr "스케줄"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "Default State"
msgstr "기본 상태"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "CxFlow Git Auto Sync"
msgstr "CxFlow Git 자동 동기화"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "Every 1 hour"
msgstr "매 1시간"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:83
msgid "**Inactive** (enable manually)"
msgstr "**비활성** (수동으로 활성화)"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:118
msgid "The cron performs two tasks:"
msgstr "크론은 두 가지 작업을 수행합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:120
msgid "Recovers stuck repos (syncing > 10 min)"
msgstr "중단된 저장소 복구 (syncing 상태 > 10분)"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:121
msgid ""
"Pulls from repos with `auto_pull_cron=True` that are in `ready` or "
"`error` state"
msgstr ""
"`ready` 또는 `error` 상태인 `auto_pull_cron=True` 저장소에서 Pull"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:123
msgid "Dependencies"
msgstr "의존성"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:125
msgid "**Python**: `PyYAML`"
msgstr "**Python**: `PyYAML`"

#: ../../cxflow/git-sync.md:126
msgid "**System**: `git` binary must be available on the server"
msgstr "**시스템**: 서버에 `git` 바이너리가 설치되어 있어야 합니다"
